482
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:29,940
Adam!

483
00:43:30,020 --> 00:43:32,310
Adam! Open the door!

484
00:43:33,020 --> 00:43:35,570
Oh, my God. Oh, God!

485
00:43:49,590 --> 00:43:51,660
Help!

486
00:43:53,760 --> 00:43:56,040
Help!

487
00:43:56,140 --> 00:43:58,670
